data.description: Adorably fantastic 4 bedroom 2.5 bath well maintained cottage style two story home on a corner lot in Summergrove sitting directly across the street from High Point Circle Park. You walk into a a wide open floor plan with hardwood floors, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, built-ins on either side of the fireplace, primary bedroom on the main with a remodeled primary bath that has oversized shower and beautiful finishes! Separate half bath and laundry room on the main as well. Upstairs has three large bedrooms and a jack and Jill bathroom with hallway access. There is also an extra long two car garage with built in storage and an unfinished and plumbed basement space just waiting for your imagination.  It's the perfect space for a home office, weight room, man cave, she shed, craft room, or anything that you can dream up! Harwood floors, Carpet is only 2 years old, Sprinkler System, Blink security system camera for the back of the house, Nest thermostats, Ring doorbell, My Q Smart Garage Video Keypad, and plenty more...This house is a must see!!
